    'body' => 'I think folks are misunderstanding the "Armorer" skill.  Under current US 
military terminology (which is the source, obviously, for a lot of 
Traveller military terminology) an armorer is someone who maintains, 
repairs, and modifies weapons.  I doubt the idea is to allow PCs to build 
battle dress -- but letting them *fix* it, or make custom modifications 
to it, is IMHO long overdue.  If this skill is what I think it is, it 
