Atlas was one of the rarer modules. It never had UWPs, although there was
some effort to produce those Sector UWP lists. I expect they are the ones
posted on the GEnie Traveller area.

There was never any formal plan to publish that list as a Module.

This listing is from the proposed Imperium Games publication schedule:

"FIRST SURVEY
This vital companion to Milieu 0 is an atlas of the 50 or so sectors that
were the Vilani Empire and its surrounding territories. The star systems of
the Sylean Federation are well defined. Farther and farther out, systems are
less well-defined. Each adventuring group determines its own survey results
for each system they visit. Lester Smith."

The concept is that this module will show the location of the star systems on
sector maps, but NOT the world data (or even the starport information). If it
has a gas giant, that would be there, as would some clue as to water/fuel
availability.

For limited regions (The Sylean Federation; The Neighborhood Of Vland, Terra)
the module would provide current information. Additional data would refer to
what was in the data banks: data now maybe 1200 to 1700 years old.


