 ::>Bribery (D)

 Default?  Hell, no!  It\'s _real_ easy to muff a bribe attempt -
 that\'s how most bribery arrests are made!

 ::>Fast Talk (D) [Refers to convincing someone to do/think something by
 ::>spurious logic and/or intellectual intimidation.]

 Persuasion.  Covers it, plus "legitimate" discourse as well.

 ::>Forensics

