Space suits can be built with WWI (or possibly even Civil War)
technology. Other than that, I agree.

>  ::>***MILITARY SKILLS*************************
> 
>  ::>Archery (C) [I do not think this should be a default skill]
>  ::> -Bow
>  ::> -Crossbow
>  ::> -Sling
>  ::> -Atlatl
