this would be a disadvantage...hmm....okay, let\'s say Hodgie, in the 
course of his adventuring career, meets up with a group of people who 
have been without outside contact for so long that they actually practice 
the supposedly dead religion he has been studying.  However, through the 
years the religion has evolved a bit, so isn\'t exactly like the religion 
he knows.  Perhaps the ref would want the player to make a task roll to 
