[This idea was shamelessly stolen from Space 1889!]

Several thousand years ago an advanced human 
society built a series of canals on Vernoa.  
The purpose of the canals was to provide 
abundant water to the dessert from melting 
polar ice.  The descendants of those ancient 
humans now live exclusively on the canals.  
Sailing skill is automatic as sail boats 
are the primary means of transportation.  
Also most children learn to swim before 
they learn to walk.

