The government of Kamdell is a very strict 
religious dictatorship based on the worship 
of a vicious marine carnivore.  Any one 
entering the ocean, for any reason, is guilty 
of trasspassing against the gods.  Penalty 
for trasspassing is death.  As a result no 
one goes for a swim here (or more importantly
no one learns to swim here).

