a Ancient planet-buster weapon, the Imperial Navy have probably
interdicted the system so that they can sift the area for scraps of
Ancient technology without treasure hunters making off with valuable
(and possibly powerful) items.

If I remember rightly, the Travellers Digest published an adventure
