    'body' => 'Jamie Young <jamie@tsc.scotnet.co.uk> writes:

> Does anyone know anything about Space Elevators (AKA Clarke Elevators)?
> I\'ve encountered them in "The Fountains of Paradise" and "Red Mars" and like
