and store them in some sort of *compact* record format. Then be able to
select the level of detail I want to see when browsing.

I think all the physical stuff (or at least *most* of it) should be
generated together, as it tends to be somewhat interdependent.

I also think we need to have routines for generating sectors (only
gives stellar type, and maybe gas gaints), routines for generating a
system given the stellar type info (including GG if the sector routines
generate that), and routines for fleshing out the system.

