    'body' => 'At 11:57 AM 6/21/96 -0400, Rich wrote:
>Ok, so what you\'re saying is that the Traveller list is for all versions of
>Traveller: CT/MT/TNE/MMT. Then Xboat is only for CT/MT, with absolutely
