    'body' => 'If it is of any use to anybody, I have written a modula-2 program on the
Amiga to generate and display star systems. The program follows the
Traveller rules - with only a couple of modifications in calculation methods
for practicality. It displays the UPP of each world, and the base temperature.

I would be happy to share the program or the code, but I must warn anyone
wanting the code that it is a bit messy. I haven\'t had time to run through
it and make it pretty.

